Usage: addModulePort [-help] <moduleName> <portName> <portDir>
                     [-bus <startId:endId>] [-moduleBased]

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
<moduleName>             # Name of hinstance or module if -moduleBased
                         # specified (string, required)
<portName>               # Name of the port (string, required)
<portDir>                # port direction, the value can be - input, output,
                         # bidi (string, required)
-bus <startId:endId>     # bus bit startId:endId (string, optional)
-moduleBased             # is module based (bool, optional)